Sentencas: The paper presents a review of thermal, flow, and material parameters from the perspective of modeling proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells (H+SOFC).
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models

Sentencas: Comments are offered regarding key parameters selected through research of the literature, featuring mostly material-related properties of electrolyte and electrodes.
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models

Sentencas: Some general relationships are proposed here for the purpose of modeling H+SOFC.
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models

Sentencas: The most important parameter is fuel cell operational temperature.
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models

Sentencas: Next to the temperature, partial pressures of hydrogen on both sides of H+SOFC impact mainly maximum voltage.
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models

Sentencas: The materials from which the fuel cell is built do not directly affect the operation of the fuel cell in the sense that they can be taken as fixed values.
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models

Sentencas: Indirectly, their influence can be seen in the resistances, that electrolyte conducts for proton flux and electrodes for electrons.
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models

Sentencas: In some cases, double ion/electron conductivity may occur.
Titulo: Key Parameters of Proton-conducting Solid Oxide Fuel Cells from the Perspective of Coherence with Models
